README

= Architecture:
The main path of data:
* Layers
	. parser:	scan given (from mem) data & and set struct pointers
	. decoder:	convert parsers's data into core's data
	. core:		mxl data storage
	. UI:		view core data
	. Print:	view core data
	. Export:	into: XML|vector(PDF|PS)|data(ODS|XLS?)HTML|bitmap(...)
* Modules
	. mxlview:	main module - dispatch + commanline; load mxl-file into mem
	. parser:	In: mem block; Out: struct of ptrs
	. decoder:	In: struct of ptrs; Out: core class object; w/ checking
	. UI:		In: core class object; Out: current gfx out
	. print:	In: core class object; Out: 
	. export:	In: core class object; Out: 
= How it's works
* Based on:
	. parser - C[/C++]
	. decoder - C++, STL?
	. core - STL only
	. UI - Qt 4.2+
	. print - ?..
	. export - ?
* compilated w/ or w/o Qt
* can B command line usable
* Structure:
	mxlview.cpp:
			<*.mxl> |
		parser.cpp >
			(parser.h) |
		decoder.cpp >
			core.h (>core.cpp) |
		toxml.cpp
* Засада:
	* parser: OK
	* decoder: ...
	* toxml: жёппа
